fields.name: Raging Vortex (C1)
fields.value: Decreases the CD of Foul Legacy: Raging Tide by 20%.

fields.name: Sweeping Gust (C3)
fields.value:
Increases the level of Gust Surge by 3.
Maximum upgrade level is 15.

fields.name: Cherishing Breezes (C4)
fields.value: Reduces DMG taken while casting Palm Vortex by 10%.

fields.name: Vortex Stellaris (C5)
fields.value:
Increases the level of Palm Vortex by 3.
Maximum upgrade level is 15.

fields.name: Intertwined Winds (C6)
fields.value:
Targets who take DMG from Gust Surge have their Anemo RES decreased by 20%.
If an Elemental Absorption occurred, then their RES towards the corresponding Element is also decreased by 20%.
